{"tid":2153013,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"官轟防暴砌詞狡辯 腦癇男脫襲警罪","createTime":"2020-08-12T09:51:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-12T12:04:07.000Z","uid":25558,"like":36,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"7687bf0d4b2c612893b324980333d13107c6b84e","tid":2153013,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T09:51:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200812/BGHMJ4F26DQ7XQPD5TNALKH54I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200812%2FBGHMJ4F26DQ7XQPD5TNALKH54I%2F&d=bHO956KQIgsLkYPN5Vvl7dVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=069a8eb5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200812%2FBGHMJ4F26DQ7XQPD5TNALKH54I%2F&h=88dced19\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200812/BGHMJ4F26DQ7XQPD5TNALKH54I/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n官轟防暴砌詞狡辯 腦癇男脫襲警罪<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】去年10月1日市民在港鐵太子站將立法會議員何君堯的相片貼在地上，有便衣警將文宣「踢甩」引發警民衝突。其間一名男子被指踢警員一腳，遭多名防暴圍毆，被控襲警罪。裁判官林子勤裁定被告是在威逼和誘導下作招認，拒接納相關紀錄呈堂，並即日裁決，批評作供警員砌詞狡辯、信口開河，並非誠實可靠的證人，裁定被告罪名不成立兼得訟費。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/HnHkz866pEBHcfNbfUY8KXcDzuM=/640x479/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KUVTGNJ5LIQYFLSWJCZWNJLNEA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FHnHkz866pEBHcfNbfUY8KXcDzuM%3D%2F640x479%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKUVTGNJ5LIQYFLSWJCZWNJLNEA.jpg&h=299ed18e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警員盧俊傑（右）被裁判官批評不誠實；左為替被告錄口供的警員李邵峰。&lt;br /&gt;資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n威逼招認 隱瞞暴打<br />\n<br />\n被告盧家業（42歲）昨就警誡供詞的自願性出庭作供，他稱自小患腦癇症需每日服藥，拘留期間曾三度要求送院；其後有防暴警。。。<br />\n。。。。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。，<span class=\"orange\">指盧習慣以「不清楚」、「唔知道」回應，避免與其他人有矛盾，如制服被告時其右方警員多番用警棍擊打被告，連盧當時都向右望，但盧竟稱看不到施襲，甚至播片後仍稱「乜都睇唔到」。</span><br />\n<br />\n林官又指，盧故意將肢體衝突的嚴重性說得比真實輕微，他堅稱只揮棍兩次，惟片段顯示他毆打被告不下十次，絕非如盧所言「先警告、揮。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：WKCC3815/19"},{"pid":"0a725106799f74c3e4722ab66732f1d2e6e601ae","tid":2153013,"uid":271176,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T09:57:13.000Z","msg":"認真問，好多單有片拍到都可以不誠實作供，冇片個d點解可以話證供可信"},{"pid":"0e683e681f4b1329611062b60434854b299f40c5","tid":2153013,"uid":25601,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T09:59:06.000Z","msg":"差佬砌生豬肉算唔算妨礙司法公正"},{"pid":"55d735758d22f2c5582ead79a8b5e8b8d6cbcfe0","tid":2153013,"uid":69544,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"0a725106799f74c3e4722ab66732f1d2e6e601ae","tid":2153013,"uid":271176,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T09:57:13.000Z","msg":"認真問，好多單有片拍到都可以不誠實作供，冇片個d點解可以話證供可信"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T09:59:21.000Z","msg":"因為紅官想點就點,你做狗就係誠實<br />\n<br />\n利申 冇讀law 等人答"},{"pid":"5442d990a6bfdb04e2dbe626501ad52f9b8084a6","tid":2153013,"uid":35930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a725106799f74c3e4722ab66732f1d2e6e601ae","tid":2153013,"uid":271176,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T09:57:13.000Z","msg":"認真問，好多單有片拍到都可以不誠實作供，冇片個d點解可以話證供可信"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T09:59:29.000Z","msg":"呢啲同雞一樣 45分鐘任砌"},{"pid":"8027e71d08637b372926c2cffd29d6d723685a8b","tid":2153013,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T10:00:18.000Z","msg":"大家要定時定候捐款去 612基金，長期作戰嚟。<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2142357\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2142357</a>"},{"pid":"eb2a9834b42367fcca8568a0e045fa2acf7613d3","tid":2153013,"uid":70786,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0e683e681f4b1329611062b60434854b299f40c5","tid":2153013,"uid":25601,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T09:59:06.000Z","msg":"差佬砌生豬肉算唔算妨礙司法公正"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T10:00:24.000Z","msg":"律政屍唔告<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"772c96